A warm evening gathering on a tropical veranda, Studio Ghibli style, featuring a diverse group of friends sharing coffee around a weathered wooden table. Soft golden lantern light illuminates faces of different ethnicities—a Nigerian man gesturing animatedly while telling a story, a Chinese woman laughing, a European man listening intently, others leaning in with genuine curiosity. Lush tropical plants frame the scene, jasmine flowers climbing wooden posts. Steam rises gently from ceramic cups. The background shows a dusky Singapore skyline through palm fronds. The atmosphere radiates genuine connection and cross-cultural exchange, with expressive character designs showing wrinkles of laughter and eyes full of warmth. Soft watercolor textures, dreamy lighting with firefly-like specks of light floating in the humid air, creating an intimate moment of human understanding across boundaries.
